    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 8pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 td {border: 1px solid #000;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 310.60387811634px;\">\n<p></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 310.6703601108px;\">\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Даъво аризаси берилаётган суднинг номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">га</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 310.60387811634px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 310.6703601108px;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">Даъвогар: </span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Даъвогарнинг номи </span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 310.60387811634px;\">\n<p></p>\n</td>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 310.6703601108px;\">\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">{#4}Даъвогарнинг юр